com.mobius.vdrapi.callbacks
Interface IHasTraceThreshold

public interface IHasTraceThreshold

A class implements IHasTraceThreshold to indicate that it will provide the trace threshold level for Document Server tracing.

Implementing this interface is optional, as the default trace threshold level is set to ViewDirectSeverityLevel.SL_DISASTER, which is the minimum server tracing level. To increase server tracing detail, implement this class and return one of the following:

ViewDirectSeverityLevel.SL_DISASTER (minimum detail),

ViewDirectSeverityLevel.SL_ERROR,

ViewDirectSeverityLevel.SL_EXCEPTION,

ViewDirectSeverityLevel.SL_WARNING or

ViewDirectSeverityLevel.SL_OK (maximum detail).

See Also:
INeedObjectWithTraceThreshold
